Sifuba s body was found in a public toilet in Khayelitsha on Monday."It is believed that the deceased was murdered at her residence in Site C Khayelitsha and her body was later moved to the public toilets " said police spokesman Captain FC Van Wyk.The case was postponed to January 5 when Sibongile Nondyolo is expected to apply for bail."These incidents are deplorable in the light of the on-going 16 Days Campaign Against Violence on Women and Children and are taken seriously by police management " said Van Wyk earlier in the week.TMG Digital/Cape Newsroom 